		<title>Mayo Clinic research may bring change to women&amp;#8217;s wrestling policies</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-research-may-bring-change-to-womens-wrestling-policies/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Helwig]]></dc:creator>
